## 三、进阶篇：切片的高级操作

### 3.1 切片克隆与复制

#### slices.Clone - 浅拷贝切片

```go
package main

import (
    "fmt"
    "slices"
)

func main() {
    original := []int{1, 2, 3, 4, 5}
    
    // Clone创建独立副本
    cloned := slices.Clone(original)
    
    fmt.Println("原始切片:", original)
    fmt.Println("克隆切片:", cloned)
    
    // 修改原切片，不影响副本
    original[0] = 100
    fmt.Println("修改后:")
    fmt.Println("原始切片:", original) // [100 2 3 4 5]
    fmt.Println("克隆切片:", cloned)   // [1 2 3 4 5]
}
```

